            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Exp. intensities I for each type of transition (E1,M1,",
                "were approximated : I=Io*(E**N), where",
                "Io - relative induced intensity,",
                "n - varied by least square method ,",
                "equal to 5.2+-0.5 for E1 transitions, 4.4+-0.9 for M1 ,",
                "for E2 was fixed as 5.",
                " Relative reduced intensities of primary gamma",
                "transitions, average for final states with given spin",
                "and parity, were obtained by data extrapolation to",
                "assumed gamma energy 7 MeV."
